<br>
&quot;Nothing that will affect our inmediate course of actions, dear friend. I will tell you later. Don't worry.&quot; he made a subtle sign pointing to the young ones that were present. Not the best time for such a weird and unbeleivable story.<br>
<br>
So the elixir had worked... probably he would have never tried it by himself. He felt better, air was again aboundant in his lungs. For three days he could be strong again, if all what he was told was true. Then... he would need more. And it wouldn't work forever! But feeling his health back, even if it was through a strange and temporary solution, filled him with joy. <br>
<br>
&quot;What's all this I have been hearing about Neo? Tell me, we don't have two missing people now, do we... Let's find Binka. There must be a connection between all our recent problems&quot; and he thought, maybe between <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>all</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> of them...  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=czakoriah>Czakoriah</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 175<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/30/04 8:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=832.topic&index=42>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Chosen Spirit</span><hr size=1> After converting some coin, Neomiah turns to leave and catches a glimpse of a male Erudite walking out the door of the bank.  Could it be? <br>
<br>
&quot;Hey Celo!&quot;<br>
<br>
Neomiah fights his way through a rush of adventurers, who are anxious to bank they raid loot.<br>
<br>
&quot;Hey watch it...Hey Celo!&quot;<br>
<br>
The Erudite stops in his tracks and turns to face the young dwarf.  Neomiah notices Celo no longer wears the colors of Chosen Spirit, and is looking at him with distaste....even hate.<br>
<br>
&quot;How you been Celo?  Tanieth and Viala said you were attacked...&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Go away dwarf or sssuffer a death unlike any you could imagine.  The being known asss Celo isss dead.  He willingly accsssepted my ssspirit.  He isss now Khlsin, the Last Iksar Enchanter...&quot;<br>
<br>
Neomiah finds the Iksar dialect humorous...<br>
<br>
&quot;Ssstop right there Khlsin...&quot;<br>
<br>
Neomiah does his best to imitate and agitate the Iksar within Celo.<br>
<br>
&quot;You're not going anywhere.&quot;<br>
<br>
The young dwarf warrior moves his hands to the hilts of his weapons.  <br>
<br>
&quot;You refuse, you will die.  I would rather my friend die by my hand than be a tortured spirit possessed by the likes of you.&quot;<br>
<br>
Khlsin snickers and begins to recite a spell.<br>
<br>
Neomiah lunges at the possessed Erudite, but misses his initial attack.  &quot;You Ssstupid Iksar!!!  It didnt have to be like this.  Neomiah presses his attack, and slices deeply into Celo's leg who winces but continues to cast his spell.  Neomiah screams and drops his weapons to grasp his head.  An evil grin spread across the Iksar Enchanter's face and he begins to cast another spell.  Neomiah convulses in pain...  <br>
<br>
Darina, a dwarven cleric and former member of Chosen Spirit saw the exchange between her former friends of which she both recognizes, and senses Celo is not about to stop until the young foolish dwarf is dead.  <br>
<br>
&quot;Hey backoff Celo!!!  You are gonna kill em!!!&quot;  <br>
<br>
Khlsin looks to Darina who has now begun to cast her own spell...<br>
<br>
&quot;Yesss...He isss about to die!&quot;<br>
<br>
Khlsin finishs weaving his final spell...<br>
<br>
Neomiah arches his back and hands recoil outward as he releases a blood curdling scream.<br>
<br>
Darina's spell lands too late...Neomiah is dead.<br>
<br>
Darina runs upto Neomiah's corpse...and cradles him in her arms...<br>
<br>
&quot;Celo, you bastard!  You killed Neo...&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Yesss...I did&quot;<br>
<br>
Khlsin begins casting another spell...<br>
<br>
Darina jumps to her feet makes ready her weapon and begins casting her own spell....<br>
<br>
Khlsin begins to laugh, and says &quot;The days of discord are coming...you will all die...&quot;<br>
<br>
Darina's spell finishes but to no effect for Khlsin has already faded away...<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
